text: Barbora Horáčková was an archer from the Czech Republic. She was born on 15 January 1969 and died on 8 April 2018. Horáčková competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics.Barbora HoráčkováBarbora HORACKOVA == References == Category:1969 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Czech archers Category:Olympians for the Czech Republic
